data.description: Attention all Buyers and Investors, Come take a look at this awesome property that offers 2 bedroom 1 bath and sits on a large PDR3 lot (per tax record) with potential to build additional units in the back. This property has a been recently painted interior/exterior and brand new septic system that was installed less than a year ago. The property is conveniently located minutes away from freeways, shopping centers, transportation, restaurants, super markets and lots more to mention. Do not miss this opportunity to own this home with all the amenities City of Palmdale has to offer!
